   "end": "6.440", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.440", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.280", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.240", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei der Lekt\u00fcre Ihrer beiden Schaufensterantr\u00e4ge ist man versucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.400", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "laut auszurufen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.320", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Willkommen in einer Friedenstraumwelt!\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.840", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Welt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.080", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "betrachtet durch die rosaroten Brillen der Gr\u00fcnen und der Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.280", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist eine Utopie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.040", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wachen Sie auf! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.440", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einerseits ist die reale Welt ganz anders. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Andererseits ist es bereits Mittagszeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.000", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir leben in einer Welt der Unsicherheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Bedrohung und eines globalen kriegerischen Terrors. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.000", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Worum geht es im Kern?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.720", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erstens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nationale Verteidigungsf\u00e4higkeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.640", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zentrale Aufgabe eines Staates ist die Gew\u00e4hrleistung der Sicherheit seiner B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.560", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also eine unabh\u00e4ngige Wehr- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.640", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Abwehrf\u00e4higkeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.680", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen R\u00fcstungsg\u00fcter zur Verteidigung und Abschreckung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zweitens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.800", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Erhalt einer eigenen wehrtechnischen Industrie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.680", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen eine deutsche Verteidigungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.200", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wehrtechnische Industrie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.240", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Oder wollen Sie deutsches Steuergeld in anderen L\u00e4ndern investieren und damit Arbeitspl\u00e4tze in unserem Land vernichten? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.000", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nat\u00fcrlich geht es in dieser Frage auch um Arbeitspl\u00e4tze. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.240", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir von der Union stehen zum Erhalt einer leistungsf\u00e4higen deutschen wehrtechnischen Industrie."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.040", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Drittens: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.520", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "B\u00fcndniszusammenhalt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.920", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben es hier schon in den unterschiedlichen Facetten geh\u00f6rt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.760", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Innerhalb der NATO und der EU arbeitet Deutschland eng mit seinen Partnern f\u00fcr Sicherheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.440", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frieden und Freiheit zusammen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.360", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das bedeutet zweierlei: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.720", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir planen gemeinsame R\u00fcstungsprojekte und produzieren dementsprechend. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.080", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber immer \u00f6fter macht das Schlagwort\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.440", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben es von Klaus-Peter Willsch schon geh\u00f6rt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.920", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eGerman free\u201c die Runde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.160", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frei \u00fcbersetzt hei\u00dft das: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man macht es lieber ohne die Deutschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil man Angst hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.920", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit uns gemeinsam entwickelte R\u00fcstungsg\u00fcter nicht verkaufen zu k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen Sie einen Ausstieg oder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "besser gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.360", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einen Ausschluss Deutschlands aus diesen Kooperationen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.560", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wollen Sie eine Isolierung Deutschlands im B\u00fcndnis? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.640", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "B\u00fcndniszusammenhalt bedeutet auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.880", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man sich als Verb\u00fcndete gegenseitig Verteidigungstechnologie nutzbar macht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um dies umzusetzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind R\u00fcstungsexporte aus Deutschland an EU-, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.920", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "NATO- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.040", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und an NATO-gleichgestellte L\u00e4nder f\u00fcr uns selbstverst\u00e4ndlich und notwendig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.840", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im R\u00fcstungsexportbericht\u00a02016 steht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.840", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Einzelausfuhrgenehmigungen in H\u00f6he von 6,85\u00a0Milliarden Euro erteilt wurden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.800", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei entfiel ein Anteil von 46,4\u00a0Prozent auf Verb\u00fcndete. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.040", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "3,67\u00a0Milliarden Euro entfielen auf Drittl\u00e4nder.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.600", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die im ersten Drittel des Jahres\u00a02017 erteilten Einzelausfuhrgenehmigungen betrugen 2,42\u00a0Milliarden Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.600", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist im Vergleich zum Vorjahreszeitraum ein Absinken um fast 30\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.760", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Anteil f\u00fcr Drittl\u00e4nder lag\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.360", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nahezu unver\u00e4ndert\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.480", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei rund 54\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.320", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich nenne hier diese konkreten Zahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.680", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die Vorredner an dieser Stelle nur herumgeschwurbelt haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.920", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir unterst\u00fctzen im Rahmen der geltenden Bestimmungen die deutsche R\u00fcstungsindustrie bei ihren Exportbem\u00fchungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.520", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so wie das auch andere europ\u00e4ische L\u00e4nder f\u00fcr ihre R\u00fcstungsindustrie tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.760", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wir sind kein Kriegswaffenmonster."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.960", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren von der links-gr\u00fcnen Opposition, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.280", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es kommt hier zu Wiederholungen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.440", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir hatten vor wenigen Wochen ein \u00e4hnliches Thema in der Aktuellen Stunde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.120", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Statt einer emotional gef\u00fchrten Debatte ist eine sachliche, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.320", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an Fakten orientierte Analyse angemessen und notwendig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "262.480", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu geh\u00f6ren zwei Wahrheiten: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "262.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "265.720", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen kein R\u00fcstungsexportkontrollgesetz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "265.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.520", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wir brauchen auch kein generelles Verbot des Exports von R\u00fcstungsg\u00fctern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.080", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei allen Ausfuhrgenehmigungen werden von der Bundesregierung die \u00f6ffentlich bekannten au\u00dfen-, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.680", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sicherheits- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.760", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und menschenrechtspolitischen Aspekte auf Grundlage des Kriegswaffenkontrollgesetzes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "283.560", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Au\u00dfenwirtschaftsverordnung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "283.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.080", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Politischen Grunds\u00e4tze der Bundesregierung und des Gemeinsamen Standpunktes des Rats der EU sorgf\u00e4ltig abgewogen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.440", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir alle wollen in einer friedlichen Welt leben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.160", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Antr\u00e4ge sind leider Ausdruck einer Realit\u00e4tsverweigerung und stellen eine sicherheitspolitische Gef\u00e4hrdung dar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "306.560", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da sie zu einer Isolierung unseres Landes innerhalb der NATO f\u00fchren w\u00fcrden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "306.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.600", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden diesen Weg nicht gehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "320.880", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden Sicherheit im B\u00fcndnis f\u00fcr unsere B\u00fcrger garantieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "320.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "322.040", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "322.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "327.000", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der n\u00e4chste Redner ist der Abgeordnete Dr.\u00a0Robby Schlund f\u00fcr die AfD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}